00:36:41,070 --> 00:36:42,760
and the school's Western suit

867
00:36:42,760 --> 00:36:43,760
looks so nice.

868
00:36:44,030 --> 00:36:46,000
Sister-in-law,
can I wear this for the wedding?

869
00:36:46,000 --> 00:36:47,110
No way.

870
00:36:47,480 --> 00:36:49,710
The groom should wear the groom's clothes.

871
00:36:49,710 --> 00:36:51,320
I've prepared them for you.

872
00:36:51,510 --> 00:36:53,110
You only get married once in life.

873
00:36:53,110 --> 00:36:54,110
Don't slack off.

874
00:36:54,110 --> 00:36:55,670
Okay, I'll listen to you.

875
00:36:58,760 --> 00:36:59,920
It's so festive.

876
00:37:01,070 --> 00:37:03,630
Sister-in-law, did you manage all this?

877
00:37:05,230 --> 00:37:06,890
Steward Liu and others did it.

878
00:37:07,230 --> 00:37:08,160
Let's go inside.

879
00:37:24,110 --> 00:37:25,150
What happened?

880
00:37:25,150 --> 00:37:26,510
This Miser Ning

881
00:37:27,400 --> 00:37:29,930
would rather lose his daughter
than his land.

882
00:37:30,190 --> 00:37:31,280
He drove me out

883
00:37:31,480 --> 00:37:32,760
and even hit my eye

884
00:37:32,880 --> 00:37:34,030
with that money bag.

885
00:37:34,480 --> 00:37:35,760
Let me see.

886
00:37:35,760 --> 00:37:36,510
Go away.

887
00:37:36,510 --> 00:37:38,170
If you went out to buy land now,

888
00:37:38,320 --> 00:37:40,070
it's thanks to our ancestors' good karma

889
00:37:40,070 --> 00:37:42,030
that you didn't get beaten up.

890
00:37:42,230 --> 00:37:43,070
Tell me.

891
00:37:43,360 --> 00:37:45,490
If something like this happened to us,

892
00:37:45,590 --> 00:37:47,670
we'd definitely work
to rescue our daughter first.

893
00:37:47,670 --> 00:37:49,030
I'd planned

894
00:37:49,030 --> 00:37:50,880
to quickly buy the land.

895
00:37:51,190 --> 00:37:53,110
I didn’t expect Miser Ning

896
00:37:53,320 --> 00:37:54,880
wouldn't even mention it.

897
00:37:55,510 --> 00:37:57,230
They have cash.

898
00:37:57,550 --> 00:37:58,630
Nonsense.

899
00:37:59,400 --> 00:38:01,510
He has 5,000 silver dollars at home

900
00:38:01,510 --> 00:38:03,370
waiting for bandits to snatch up?

901
00:38:03,880 --> 00:38:06,340
Then why didn't he
sell the land to raise money?

902
00:38:06,340 --> 00:38:08,470
Anyway, it'll be good for his daughter

903
00:38:09,030 --> 00:38:10,710
to stay with the bandits.

904
00:38:12,510 --> 00:38:14,040
What are you talking about?

905
00:38:14,110 --> 00:38:15,400
Something big happened.

906
00:38:15,400 --> 00:38:17,230
The bride Xiuxiu

907
00:38:17,710 --> 00:38:18,670
got kidnapped

908
00:38:18,670 --> 00:38:20,630
by Chicken Ridge's bandits.

909
00:38:22,590 --> 00:38:23,650
What are you doing?

910
00:38:23,960 --> 00:38:25,840
He's going to watch the show.

911
00:38:31,440 --> 00:38:32,640
Mole Cricket's here.

912
00:38:32,760 --> 00:38:34,710
With Mole Cricket here,

913
00:38:34,710 --> 00:38:36,760
the land deed will be done right.

914
00:38:37,480 --> 00:38:39,000
Let’s see if Ning Xuexiang

915
00:38:39,000 --> 00:38:41,330
will sell the land to redeem his daughter.

916
00:38:44,510 --> 00:38:45,590
Xueshi is here.

917
00:38:48,280 --> 00:38:50,880
I came as soon as I heard the news.

918
00:38:51,320 --> 00:38:53,840
Xuexiang, sell the land now!

919
00:38:54,280 --> 00:38:56,630
Many people in the village
came to me.

920
00:38:56,960 --> 00:38:58,150
They had me come ask.

921
00:38:58,400 --> 00:38:59,760
If you want to do it,

922
00:38:59,790 --> 00:39:01,190
I'll find a buyer for you.

923
00:39:01,480 --> 00:39:01,920
Look.

924
00:39:02,190 --> 00:39:03,150
I've even brought over

925
00:39:03,150 --> 00:39:05,710
the documents for writing a land deed.

926
00:39:13,630 --> 00:39:15,440
Xiuxiu really got kidnapped by bandits?

927
00:39:15,440 --> 00:39:16,360
Of course.

928
00:39:16,550 --> 00:39:18,360
Xiuxiu is really done for now.

929
00:39:20,630 --> 00:39:21,880
You bastard!

930
00:39:22,840 --> 00:39:24,070
Are you still a Ning?

931
00:39:24,710 --> 00:39:26,550
How could you do such an evil thing?

932
00:39:26,550 --> 00:39:27,150
Hey,

933
00:39:27,800 --> 00:39:30,110
what do you mean?

934
00:39:30,110 --> 00:39:31,630
You won't sell the land?

935
00:39:31,880 --> 00:39:32,840
You have money?

936
00:39:33,120 --> 00:39:34,650
It's none of your business.

937
00:39:34,670 --> 00:39:35,590
Get out!

938
00:39:40,150 --> 00:39:42,240
You're unreasonable!

939
00:39:44,030 --> 00:39:44,590
Wolves!

940
00:39:44,610 --> 00:39:46,670
You are just a bunch of greedy wolves!

941
00:39:46,920 --> 00:39:48,670
Listen, that's not the land.

942
00:39:48,800 --> 00:39:50,230
It's my blood! My flesh!

943
00:39:50,230 --> 00:39:51,110
My life!

944
00:39:52,190 --> 00:39:53,990
You all want a bite at any chance.

945
00:39:54,030 --> 00:39:55,230
A bunch of you!

946
00:39:55,800 --> 00:39:58,000
Dream on!

947
00:39:59,150 --> 00:40:01,680
How can you save her
without selling the land?

948
00:40:03,110 --> 00:40:05,510
He's still not selling the land
to save her.

949
00:40:05,760 --> 00:40:06,670
After tonight,

950
00:40:06,880 --> 00:40:08,400
his daughter will be ruined.

951
00:40:08,400 --> 00:40:09,710
Yeah, seriously.

952
00:40:10,880 --> 00:40:11,840
What a pity.

953
00:40:12,630 --> 00:40:13,670
Seriously.

954
00:40:15,270 --> 00:40:16,140
Disperse.

955
00:40:21,280 --> 00:40:21,760
Here.

956
00:40:21,920 --> 00:40:22,950
Put this on.

957
00:40:23,360 --> 00:40:24,160
It looks good.

958
00:40:26,150 --> 00:40:27,070
If it doesn't fit,

959
00:40:27,070 --> 00:40:28,510
we have to tailor it quickly.

960
00:40:28,510 --> 00:40:29,760
The city folks

961
00:40:29,790 --> 00:40:30,830
like to wear

962
00:40:30,850 --> 00:40:32,510
suits and wedding dresses now.

963
00:40:32,510 --> 00:40:33,320
They really look nice.

964
00:40:33,320 --> 00:40:34,580
After you get married,

965
00:40:34,670 --> 00:40:36,440
you can have
whatever modern style you want.

966
00:40:36,440 --> 00:40:37,400
Not today.

967
00:40:37,630 --> 00:40:39,360
The ancestors are watching.

968
00:40:39,550 --> 00:40:41,080
We have to follow the rules.

969
00:40:42,900 --> 00:40:43,900
Let me see.

970
00:40:47,510 --> 00:40:48,240
Looks great.

971
00:40:48,510 --> 00:40:50,150
Master. Master!

972
00:40:52,020 --> 00:40:53,550
I heard that Eldest Young Master

973
00:40:53,550 --> 00:40:55,320
got kicked out by Chairman Chu

974
00:40:55,320 --> 00:40:57,220
and is going up the mountain
to save Xiuxiu himself.

975
00:40:57,220 --> 00:40:58,660
He took his men

976
00:40:59,110 --> 00:40:59,920
on a shortcut

977
00:41:00,070 --> 00:41:01,600
and are already going west.

978
00:41:01,670 --> 00:41:02,800
Oh no.

979
00:41:03,920 --> 00:41:05,030
This fool!

980
00:41:05,030 --> 00:41:07,110
He's really on a suicide mission.

981
00:41:07,510 --> 00:41:09,780
Father, think of a way!

982
00:41:09,920 --> 00:41:11,780
So what if you lose your daughter?

983
00:41:11,800 --> 00:41:14,090
You can't lose Kejin too!

984
00:41:14,200 --> 00:41:15,800
Lianye, what are you talking about?

985
00:41:15,800 --> 00:41:17,200
You foul-mouthed woman.

986
00:41:17,340 --> 00:41:19,530
How have we lost Xiuxiu?

987
00:41:19,560 --> 00:41:21,730
Mother, I'm worried.

988
00:41:21,760 --> 00:41:23,840
I want Father to think of a solution.

989
00:41:24,230 --> 00:41:24,920
Honey,

990
00:41:25,770 --> 00:41:27,450
if you don't sell the land,

991
00:41:27,920 --> 00:41:29,520
I'll go to the bandits' lair.

992
00:41:29,660 --> 00:41:30,920
I'll save my daughter.

993
00:41:31,100 --> 00:41:32,310
If I can't save her,

994
00:41:32,360 --> 00:41:34,150
my daughter and I will die together.

995
00:41:34,150 --> 00:41:35,150
Mother! Mother!

996
00:41:35,150 --> 00:41:36,360
Don't be angry, Mother.

997
00:41:36,360 --> 00:41:38,110
Mother, don't be angry.

998
00:41:38,960 --> 00:41:40,020
What are you doing?

999
00:41:40,130 --> 00:41:41,290
Don't be unreasonable.

1000
00:41:41,290 --> 00:41:42,400
She's my daughter too.

1001
00:41:42,400 --> 00:41:43,860
I'm just as worried as you.

1002
00:41:47,110 --> 00:41:47,920
All right.

1003
00:41:52,150 --> 00:41:53,320
I'll go back to my room

1004
00:41:53,320 --> 00:41:54,780
to get the land deed's box.

1005
00:41:55,290 --> 00:41:57,220
I'll sell the land and raise money.

1006
00:42:00,080 --> 00:42:01,600
You two must be tired.

1007
00:42:01,920 --> 00:42:02,760
Go back now.

1008
00:42:05,150 --> 00:42:07,950
I'm going back to my room
to get the land deed's box.

1009
00:42:11,150 --> 00:42:11,750
Xuexiang,

1010
00:42:12,030 --> 00:42:13,630
call me if you need anything.

1011
00:42:14,030 --> 00:42:15,690
Sister-in-law, I'm leaving.

1012
00:42:31,360 --> 00:42:32,320
You coward.

1013
00:42:32,590 --> 00:42:33,650
Why don't you go in?

1014
00:42:35,030 --> 00:42:36,190
I'm not in a hurry.

1015
00:42:36,670 --> 00:42:38,230
I'm worried for the girl.

1016
00:42:38,920 --> 00:42:40,320
It’s getting dark.

1017
00:42:40,960 --> 00:42:43,230
Is Miser Ning really not going to
ransom her?

1018
00:42:43,230 --> 00:42:44,540
She's his daughter.

1019
00:42:44,630 --> 00:42:46,480
He's gotta ransom her no matter what.

1020
00:42:46,480 --> 00:42:48,610
Besides, Miser Ning has 700 mu of land.

1021
00:42:48,670 --> 00:42:49,440
Da Zong,

1022
00:42:49,880 --> 00:42:51,070
I have a favor to ask.

1023
00:42:51,070 --> 00:42:52,320
If no one comes

1024
00:42:52,550 --> 00:42:54,150
and Second Boss finishes up,

1025
00:42:54,590 --> 00:42:56,190
you gotta let me have my go.

1026
00:42:56,760 --> 00:42:58,230
You go tell Second Boss.

1027
00:42:58,400 --> 00:42:59,730
We’ll all go easy on you.

1028
00:42:59,840 --> 00:43:01,230
How dare I?